summary: Everyone brushes off the fact that Dany burns all the food from the Reach while I'm here, as an agriculturalist (soon to be),...
body: Everyone brushes off the fact that Dany burns all the food from the Reach while I’m here, as an agriculturalist (soon to be), being triggered and wringing my hair out. People don’t know how scarce food can be, esp when you’re in a middle of war.

summary: For those who have seen the game of thrones live concert experience: the last song they play, the game of thrones main titles...
body: For those who have seen the game of thrones live concert experience: the last song they play, the game of thrones main titles but sort of redone, when I was watching it I totally had the thought of “oh shit this could be the last song they play on the show”, like the outro or whatever. Then it got me thinking about it ending and the music and I AM NOT READY FOR IT TO END 😭 game of thrones has been a huge part of my imagination since 2013. That’s almost a quarter of my life, and all of my adult life. It’s such a huge huge part of me and I’m not ready to let it go.
